title: Juicy Brew - Kaimuki (Open Late March)
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, American, International, Fast food, Juice bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Its 2nd outlet, open March 2016. The daily menu changes based farm produce. Offers a variety of breakfast and lunch sandwiches, side salads, chilled desserts, baked goods, coffee, tea, and cold pressed juice. Veg items are prepared in a separate station.
